<plot>A trio of tales set in recession-era Kuala Lumpur. Tale 1 : A lone sniper, Ah Loong (Tan Eng Heng) befriends a red bean soup seller (Soo-Anne Gooi) and tries to redeem his violent past. Tale 2 : Steve (Pang Khee Teik), a retrenched worker is obsessed when he finds the rifle dumped by Ah Loong. Tale 3 : Restaurant-owner (Huzir Sulaiman), owing a gambling debt to thugs, is forced to pull a hit for them when he can't settle up. A mysterious, charismatic gun dealer (Paul Lau) links the tales.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503298</url></doc>
